# Frontend Development Rules Index

**Purpose**: Router for frontend rules - detects keywords and routes to language indexes or framework files.

**Chaining**: Root Router → This Index (Router) → Language Router/Index → Framework/Subcategory Index → Files

**Graph Structure**: This is a Layer 2 node that routes to Layer 1 nodes (language/framework indexes) based on keywords.

