## Loading Pattern

**Router → This Index → Language Router/Index → Framework/Subcategory → Files**

1. Root Router detects "frontend" or framework keyword → loads this index
2. This index routes to language router/index or framework file
3. Language router/index routes to subcategory indexes
4. Subcategory indexes point to specific rule files

